```

## Disclaimer

This tool is intended for educational purposes and for use on networks you own or have explicit permission to monitor. Capturing network traffic without authorization may be illegal in your jurisdiction.

## Possible Future Improvements

- Live protocol statistics / top talkers summary
- Export captures to `.pcap` format for use in Wireshark
- GUI built with Tkinter or a web dashboard
- Alerting on suspicious traffic patterns

